OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784908087
OL,3,CParents warned as unsafe children's
OL,4,Ctoys seized from shops
OL,6,FImitations of products including
OL,7,F'Squishy Dumpings' and 'NeeDoh' were
OL,8,Fspotted in various shops, but without
OL,9,Fthe legally required information which
OL,10,Fshows where the toys came from and who
OL,11,Fimported them. In several cases,
OL,12,Fofficers were worried by strong
OL,13,Fchemical smells coming from some of
OL,14,Fthe gel-filled toys.
OL,16,FIn a caution to parents, Reading
OL,17,FTrading Standards told shoppers to
OL,18,Fwatch out for toys which didn't have
OL,19,Fthe right safety information - a
OL,20,F'UKCA' or 'CE' marking - as they could
OL,21,Fbe a safety risk.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784908087
OL,3,CParents warned as unsafe children's
OL,4,Ctoys seized from shops
OL,6,FWhile the toys might look harmless,
OL,7,Fthe authority said, they could pose a
OL,8,Freal danger to children.
OL,10,FCllr Finn McGoldrick, Lead Member for
OL,11,FEnvironmental Services and Community
OL,12,FSafety, said: "Parents and carers
OL,13,Fshould be able to trust that the toys
OL,14,Fthey buy for their children are safe.
OL,16,F"These product seizures demonstrate
OL,17,Four ongoing commitment to protecting
OL,18,Fconsumers and removing potentially
OL,19,Fdangerous products from the
OL,20,Fmarketplace."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784908087
OL,3,CParents warned as unsafe children's
OL,4,Ctoys seized from shops
OL,6,FHe added: "During the summer holidays,
OL,7,FI would ask people to remain vigilant
OL,8,Fand make sure any toys purchased are
OL,9,Ffrom reputable retailers, that you
OL,10,Fcheck for the appropriate safety
OL,11,Fmarkings, and report any concerns
OL,12,Fabout unsafe products to our Trading
OL,13,FStandards team."
OL,15,FReading Trading Standards is
OL,16,Fcontinuing to carry out shop visits
OL,17,Facross the borough looking for
OL,18,Fimitation and dangerous toys. It also
OL,19,Fwarned businesses that they could face
OL,20,Fenforcement action if they're found to
OL,21,Fbe in breach of safety standards.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
